{"tid":1657883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[呀仔呢?] 警員佐級協會申禁公佈完整選民名冊 法庭拒批臨時禁令但下令暫停查冊","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T07:34:51.000Z","uid":63452,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"46f226f166b8f5d0f4f49bc8acca61657ad5a866","tid":1657883,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:44:36.000Z","msg":"警察員佐級協會日前向高等法院申請司法覆核，指<span style=\"color: red;\">選民登記冊同時公開選民姓名和住址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>的做法侵犯私隱，尤其近期警察遭到大規模「起底」，要求法庭裁定違憲並頒下臨時禁制令。高院法官周家明下午閉門聆訊後，<span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕臨時禁制令申請</span>，惟准許申請方於本周五前決定是否上訴，故下令由現在開始直至該限期屆滿為止，公眾及候選人均暫時不准查閱選民登記冊。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n原告解釋申請本案的原因，是鑑於近來公眾惡意和大量地搜尋發發佈警務人員的私人資訊，俗稱「起底」，對警察和家人的私生活及人身安全構成威脅。原告指自6月起一連串反修例示威造成警民對立，警察受到大量辱罵、口頭威脅和滋擾，在Facebook、Twitter、連登等社交媒體和網上討論區有大量起底行為，例如連結多達15萬人的「老豆搵仔」Telegram群組。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n申請書指，根據《選舉管理委員會（選民登記）（立法會地方選區）（區議會選區）規例》第20和21條，<span style=\"color: red;\">選管會必須提供全份選民登記冊供公眾在指定地點查閱，包含選民姓名及住址，並可在應任何人申請而酌情提供登記冊的摘錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>。公眾須獲選管會批准後，才可在查閱登記冊時抄錄、記錄或複製內容，選舉後兩周內須銷毀內容，<span style=\"color: red;\">而為了無關選舉之目的而複製選民資料屬刑事罪行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Source :  <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191016&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60159482\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191016%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60159482&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=70edf1ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191016%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60159482&h=929fa4b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191016&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60159482</a></span>"},{"pid":"012c03dd513421cd2a3d8def89ade624f0c97592","tid":1657883,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"62ae1b804974ed3d1d8b351dfa50390511e745a2","tid":1657883,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e79e55757e0d1e9ec384acbcaa053d3b6993dd1","tid":1657883,"uid":63452,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"真係佢唔講都無人知有啲咁嘅德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d094da4c5398af487022ef2aabb515480e58209d","tid":1657883,"uid":810,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"藍絲: 好人好者怕咩比人睇"},{"pid":"9daaea11a35061434b011097c6b809f117696fce","tid":1657883,"uid":288707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"法官先唔想因為你班契弟搞到走唔到佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7622d8098def5b5655b156bafc21f3be685c1b","tid":1657883,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855c6b81b8acf2d86243aaa697d759bcbff03cfe","tid":1657883,"uid":37869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"「故下令由現在開始